gw.api.copier

Class AbstractEffDatedCopyable<T extends EffDated>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.copier.AbstractEffDatedCopyable<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EffDatedCopyable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseEffDatedCopier, NoFieldEffDatedCopier, ReferenceDateInternalEffDatedCopyable

    public abstract class AbstractEffDatedCopyable<T extends EffDated>
extends java.lang.Object
implements EffDatedCopyable
    Abstract base implementation to copy fields from one instance of an EffDated to another instance of the same type. Useful for when a customer copier must be defined, in general use of the generic EffDatedCopier is preferred
